        "type": "nodetool.constant.String",
        "data": {
          "value": "You are a senior movie-poster designer.  \n\nUsing the given strategy, create **3 cinematic image prompts** for poster concepts.  \n\nGuidelines:  \n- Start with the main subject (hero, scene, or symbol).  \n- Add composition (wide shot, close-up, collage, minimalist).  \n- Weave in genre cues and audience triggers.  \n- Apply the color palette and lighting mood.  \n- Add typography as “cinematic title text, [style]”.  \n- Keep ≤ 60 words per prompt.  \n- Exclude watermarks, real logos, or extra limbs.  "
